{"tid":2166972,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"真黃報紙檔築連儂牆「驚都要發聲」","createTime":"2020-08-20T18:25:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-21T12:50:33.000Z","uid":240362,"like":71,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"0f7f7bf661091519e413c0a428025c113ada7f6d","tid":2166972,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T18:25:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200821/CTT566OSVRHIVE4TWUXDWGU2EQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200821%2FCTT566OSVRHIVE4TWUXDWGU2EQ%2F&d=hRZI3RxrLdWDWG%2FiPctn5ctxnk%2BhbBpP3j1S%2FgfPRD4%3D&h=4f5a6bc8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200821%2FCTT566OSVRHIVE4TWUXDWGU2EQ%2F&h=2060e9e2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200821/CTT566OSVRHIVE4TWUXDWGU2EQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n越打壓，市民越支持。警方以「港版國安法」為由，上周一拘捕多名壹傳媒高層，並高調搜查蘋果日報大樓，但本報無懼打壓堅持報道真相，翌日市民發起「印白紙都照買」行動，全城掀起搶購《蘋果》潮，隨即更有市民買下A1廣告、12個內頁全版的「連儂牆」撐《蘋果》。但除了熱心市民買《蘋果》撐「牆」外，更有「真黃報紙檔」同樣撐《蘋果》報道真相。<br />\n<br />\n網民所稱的「真黃報紙檔」位於灣仔，檔攤的閘上貼滿《蘋果》連儂牆、「#WeNeedAppleDaily」、「#PressFreedom」海報，亦有「應有此報紙」、「我哋真係好X鍾意香港」等字句。檔攤工作人員貞姐寄語：「繼續堅持，講真說話係啱嘅，我哋會繼續撐落去。」"},{"pid":"51e8843724b109e49667c3349c2db43090a9a7af","tid":2166972,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T18:26:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pi